column5: Went up north into the woods.  Had a net man/camera man this time. Armed with lures made by board member Misfish.  One lure caught lakers, bass and white fish.  Caught some real nice ones. Drove around in the boat about 80miles. Had great company so not much talking to myself.  One night it was  almost 0deg.  I had to get up at 2 am and hook up a new propane tank.  Almost froze it was so cold.
That would be the creature one. Nice work bud.
In general terms., where the heck were you?  Fall weather, bring it on! Doug
Drive straight north. Check the temps.   It’s cold up there.
